name: Bomb launcher
description: Shoots a bomb which explodes on impact, damaging nearby enemies

name: Atomic bombs
description: Increased damage and blast radius, replaces effect with chemical burn

name: Upward launcher
description: Increased range, and bombs travel above enemies to target

name: Missile launcher
description: Massive range, shoots missiles which hone onto targets

name: Triple launcher
description: Shoots 3 missiles at once. Special targeting mode means that each missile will target different enemies

name: Silo
description: Increased range, shoots individual bombs but 7x as fast

name: Super Silo
description: Shoots better missiles, increased range, slightly faster than before

name: Stun bomb
description: Stuns enemies, and more knockback and damage

name: Black hole bomb
description: Bombs create a black hole which stuns even resistant enemies and draws them to the center
